        <font color="midnightblue" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> My story is much darker. See I was a young recruit in the Academy and good at my job. But one day I saw something I could not hide so I committed the ultimate sin and testified in the High Courts of Camelot against other Mages in the academy who had gone bad. These Mages then tried to kill me but got the woman I loved instead. Framed for a murder now I prowl the Frontiers. An outlaw hunting outlaws, a bounty hunter a Renegade.</P><P>One day while tracking a couple of rotten Mages trying to extort this Circus run by a man named Stenchy. He took me in for I had not eaten in days. While sleeping in Sir Toadstools tent, great show by the way he was a Paladin but came down with some rare skin condition. These 3 Mages starting blasting the tent. I got out in time to save myself and Sir Toadstool to see the circus being burned down and Stenchy barely alive.</P><P>I vowed from that day forward to help rebuild the circus and protect Stenchy from harm.</P><P></P><P><img src="http://www.bennettsonline.net/images/azzameen.gif" border=0></P><P>Edited by - azzameen on 05/18/2002  07:37:47</P><P>Edited by - azzameen on 05/18/2002  07:38:11<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
